Prebon

Prebon was liking Spears' behaviour. Watching Spears kiss him must be 
making Striker lose all hopee. Prebon eally had no interest in Spears 
because he had a bot back home, but he would do anything to see bots 
suffer. And on top of that, Spears didn't even realize that she was 
hurting Striker.

"Yes, let us go to the bridge, so we can map out how to get Ramulus."

He kissed her on the cheek, laughin on the inside about Striker, took 
her by the arm and started walking towards the bridge.
